  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Base Camp bar and restaurant is only 100 metres away and offers a continental buffet breakfast and a three course dinner in the evenings. The restaurant serves classic Italian food, and the pizzas are the real deal. The bar sells a selection of local and international wines, beers, soft drinks and coffee.</p>
<p>If you are self-catering, the site has its own delicatessen which sells the basics, from milk, bread and pasta to pre-cooked meals. It opens from 7.30am-11pm.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
