  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Woody Studios </strong>are around 35m² and sleep up to three people on pull-out beds and a single sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Woody Apartments </strong>are around 55m² and sleep up to four people and have a balcony. They have one bedroom with double bed and communal area with two pull-out single beds. These apartments come with a second bathroom.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Kitchen with oven/microwave, fridge, toaster, kettle and coffee maker</li>
<li>Sky TV</li>
<li>Shower</li>
